First Name
Last Name
Username
Email or Phone
Password
Password Confirmation

Default role:

student

Only admins can assign:

teacher
admin
Password Security

Passwords are never stored as plain text.

Django uses:

PBKDF2

with unique salt for every password.

JWT Authentication

Authentication uses:

Access Token
Refresh Token

Architecture:

Access Token
Short Lifetime

Refresh Token
Long Lifetime
Advanced Token Security

The system implements:

Refresh Token Rotation

Every refresh operation:

Old Refresh Token → Invalid
New Refresh Token → Issued
Token Blacklisting

Invalidated tokens are added to blacklist.

Used for:

Logout
Session termination
Security protection
Device Tracking System

Every login request sends:

x-device-id
x-device-name

Device ID is generated on frontend and stored in:

localStorage
Device Database

Table:

