Stores:

device_id
device_name
ip_address
user_agent
last_login_at
is_active
Session Tracking System

Table:

security_usersession

Stores:

user
device
refresh_token
ip_address
user_agent
created_at
last_seen_at
is_active
Session Rules

Maximum devices:

2

Maximum active sessions:

1

Behavior:

Same device login

Old session is closed.

New session is created.

Login allowed.

Different device login

If another active session exists:

Login blocked

Purpose:

Prevent account sharing
